        <body>
            <div type="question">
                <p>Imagine your life in 10 years time. What will it look like?</p>
                <note type="word-limit">(at least 60 words)</note>
                <label type="level">
                    <span>A2</span>
                </label>
            </div>
            <div type="answer">
                <p>I'm keen on the mountains, specialy The Alpes. And my dream would be living there. I imagine the fixture and furniture in a pretty chalet or flat, front of a majestic vieuw. I often could walking in this marvelous scenary. Sometimes, friends and especcialy my children would come for some stays. They could be accomodated at our home, of course. I must be patient and keep hope. Time will tell us.</p>
            </div>
